        <div class="faqTitle_wrap">
            <h2>
                Frequently Asked Questions
            </h2>
        </div>


        <div class="faqWrap">

            <div class="faqItem">
                <h3> 
                    What is Terror Hub?                   
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Terror Hub is a platform dedicated to horror enthusiasts. Users can submit their own horror stories, explore Creepy Pastas, engage in forum discussions, and even predict their lifespan with the Death Clock.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faqItem">
                <h3>
                    How do I submit a story?                    
                </h3>
                <p>
                    To submit a story, simply navigate to the " <a href="/terrorTales/submission">Create Story</a> " section on the website. Make sure to adhere to the submission guidelines and agree to the terms and conditions before submitting.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faqItem">
                <h3>   
                    Can I write my own Creepy Pasta?                 
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Absolutely! Terror Hub welcomes original Creepy Pastas. You can craft your story and <a href="/terrorTales/submission">submit</a> it through the dedicated Creepy Pasta section.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faqItem">
                <h3>   
                    How does the Death Clock work?                 
                </h3>
                <p>
                    The <a href="/deathClock/questions">Death Clock</a> is an intriguing feature where users can answer a series of questions designed to predict their lifespan. The results are based on real-life data, adding a unique twist to the experience.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faqItem">
                <h3>  
                    Are there any age restrictions?                  
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Yes, users must be at least 18 years old to use certain features like story submissions and accessing specific content areas. Make sure to check the website's <a href="/disclaimer">disclaimer</a> for more details.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faqItem">
                <h3>  
                    How are stories moderated?                  
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Stories undergo a moderation process to ensure they adhere to community guidelines. Content that violates the <a href="/disclaimer">guidelines</a> or is deemed inappropriate will not be approved for publication.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faqItem">
                <h3>   
                    Can I interact with other users?                 
                </h3>
                <p>
                    Absolutely! Terror Hub encourages community engagement. Users can like, comment, and share stories, participate in forum discussions, and even connect with like-minded horror enthusiasts.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faqItem">
                <h3>   
                    How often is the content updated?                 
                </h3>
                <p>
                    New stories, Creepy Pastas, and forum discussions are added regularly. The website aims to provide fresh content to keep users engaged and the horror community thriving.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="faqItem">
                <h3> 
                    I have more questions. How can I contact support?                   
                </h3>
                <p>
                    For any additional questions or support inquiries, you can reach out to our support team through the contact page. We're here to help!
                </p>
            </div>

